              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-display mb-2 text-gray-900">Technical E-commerce SEO</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Resolve duplicate content issues, optimize faceted navigation, implement proper canonicalization,
                  manage pagination, and optimize crawl budget for large catalogs.
